text: Jean-Pierre Urbing (22 July 1899 - 3 May 1975) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1899 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
